3. SOLUTION OVERVIEW
================================================================================

The Lead Management System provides a web-based dashboard where users can:

  - Capture new leads with contact details, source, and initial status
  - View, edit, update, and delete lead records (role-dependent)
  - Assign or reassign leads to sales representatives
  - Schedule and complete follow-up activities (calls, demos, emails)
  - Convert qualified leads into customers with company and revenue details
  - View real-time analytics dashboards (total leads, revenue, workload distribution)
  - Run stored procedure analytics per sales representative
  - Maintain a complete activity log (audit trail) for accountability

Key DBMS features demonstrated:
  - Relational schema with primary keys and foreign key constraints
  - One-to-many and one-to-one relationships
  - Database TRIGGER for automatic audit logging on lead creation
  - STORED PROCEDURE for representative performance analytics
  - Referential integrity with ON DELETE CASCADE / SET NULL rules
  - Dual database support (SQLite for development, MySQL for submission)


