The ER model consists of 6 entities and their relationships:

ENTITIES:
---------

  DEPARTMENT
    Attributes: dept_id (PK), dept_name, dept_head, location
    Description: Organizational unit that groups sales representatives

  SALES_REPRESENTATIVE
    Attributes: rep_id (PK), name, email, phone, designation, dept_id (FK)
    Description: Sales team member who manages and follows up on leads

  LEAD
    Attributes: lead_id (PK), first_name, last_name, email, phone, source,
               status, assigned_to (FK), created_at, updated_at
    Description: Central entity — a prospective customer in the sales pipeline

  CUSTOMER
    Attributes: customer_id (PK), lead_id (FK, UNIQUE), company_name, address,
               conversion_date, total_value
    Description: A lead that has been successfully converted to a paying customer

  FOLLOW_UP
    Attributes: followup_id (PK), lead_id (FK), rep_id (FK), followup_date,
               remarks, next_followup_date, status
    Description: Scheduled or completed follow-up activity on a lead

  ACTIVITY_LOG
    Attributes: log_id (PK), lead_id (FK), rep_id (FK), action, action_date,
               description
    Description: Audit trail recording all significant actions on leads


RELATIONSHIPS:
--------------

  DEPARTMENT ──(1:N)──► SALES_REPRESENTATIVE
    One department has many sales representatives.
    Each representative belongs to one department (optional).

  SALES_REPRESENTATIVE ──(1:N)──► LEAD
    One representative can be assigned many leads.
    Each lead is assigned to at most one representative.

  LEAD ──(1:1)──► CUSTOMER
    A lead can convert to exactly one customer record.
    Each customer record maps to exactly one lead (enforced by UNIQUE on lead_id).

  LEAD ──(1:N)──► FOLLOW_UP
    One lead can have many follow-up records.
    Each follow-up belongs to one lead.

  SALES_REPRESENTATIVE ──(1:N)──► FOLLOW_UP
    One representative can perform many follow-ups.
    Each follow-up is associated with one representative.

  LEAD ──(1:N)──► ACTIVITY_LOG
    One lead can have many activity log entries.

  SALES_REPRESENTATIVE ──(1:N)──► ACTIVITY_LOG
    One representative can appear in many log entries.


